content: Hi I recently did a training for the mobile inbox team on last Tuesday. But I haven't be able to receive access to the digital-corr-start here or the mobile inbox. I was really interested in starting to volunteer this week for the campaigns
Hi <@1288289159416643707> if you click on Channels & Roles near the top of the main menu and choose Respond to Voter Inquiries, digit-corr-start-here will open.
I've tried doing that and it is not opening for me. I'm only able to see mobile inbox and email inbox resources but nothing else
that shows at "no access" for me, probably same for Jalan
Yes I see the "no access" channel
Yes that's what it shows for me
We had a security update yesterday, and it closed of a lot of thing. We are working to fix that now.
I opened mobile inbox for you. I still can't get the digi-corr-start-here, but I think you only need that to choose the mobile-inbox
Thanks so much I'm able to see it now! Truly appreciate your assistance
Thank you for volunteering, you are doing great work!
One last thing is it possible to be added the  scale to win or sent an invite link to my email it saying I can't do the campaigns because I'm not accepted

Hi Jalan, Scale to Win is outside of the Discord, you set up an account on the Scale to Win page and then you connect that to the texting campaigns that we facilitate. you can get more info from https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1266829704204386334 let me know if you cant see that channel.
